value.name: DirecTV users unable to login (205.4 error) or reset password - PiunikaWeb
value.snippet: 1:36 pm (IST): Now, DirecTV team has acknowledged the issue where many users are unable to login to their accounts due to ‘205.4 error’. A fix is in development, but there is no ETA for its rollout yet. PiunikaWeb started as purely an investigative tech journalism website with main focus on ‘breaking’ or ‘exclusive’ news.

value.name: ‎CARE CODE: 205.4 | AT&T Community Forums

I had to call customer services about 3 time, first 2 the IVR disconnected my call and the 3rd time I got through and met a nice lady who worked tirelessly to help me resolve.

value.name: 21 CFR § 205.4 - LII / Legal Information Institute
value.snippet: Every wholesale distributor in a State who engages in wholesale distributions of prescription drugs in interstate commerce must be licensed by the State licensing authority in accordance with this part before engaging in wholesale distributions of prescription drugs in interstate commerce.
